column34: Hi I am Santana Rodriguez and I am absolutely heartbroken as are many others of the injustice that Disney did to Johnny Depp. Disney fired Johnny Depp because of a false accusation with Amber Heard and they didn’t bother to listen to the case first. They essentially turned their back on a beloved actor. They’re trying to make a new movie without Johnny Depp. They will essentially replace him like nothing. We need to boycott this movie because of Disney’s disrespect to Johnny. Disney should not make a movie without Johnny, but they will anyways. We the fans of Pirates of the Caribbean and Johnny Depp can change this. If we come together and boycott this movie, we could potentially get Disney to cancel the project and let the franchise rest. If we win, Johnny Depp will get the justice he deserves from Disney. If Disney wins, they will get nothing but money from milking a franchise that deserves to rest.
